141
00:09:42,930 --> 00:09:44,100
Princezna Emeraude?

142
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,180
Ale...

143
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:49,180
Princezna Emeraude je vězněna Zagatem...

144
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:51,390
