00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:22,780
Ne!

229
00:16:22,990 --> 00:16:24,490
Příšery, co jsem nemohla zničit...

230
00:16:37,470 --> 00:16:37,920
Hikaru!

231
00:16:38,010 --> 00:16:38,470
Fuu!

232
00:16:38,510 --> 00:16:39,510
Vzbuďte se!

233
00:16:40,970 --> 00:16:42,930
Popadněte ty holky támhle!

